# UI text in English

All user-facing text in this project must be in **English**.

- **Labels, buttons, titles, descriptions**: use English (e.g. "Last updated", "API available", "Sendingâ€¦").
- **Error and status messages**: use English (e.g. "Network error", "Offline", "Metadata unavailable").
- **HTML**: set `lang="en"` on the root element; use English in `title`, `meta description`, and visible content.
- **Comments in UI/frontend code** may stay in any language; this rule targets text shown to end users.

When adding or changing copy in `public/` (HTML, JS, etc.), write it in English so the principle is not forgotten.
